{"tid":1668622,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"加泰獨立定香港雙普選機會大啲","createTime":"2019-10-22T05:47:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-23T01:54:06.000Z","uid":81270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b66a0b81b76d6f8255ecec714aca37e7b0b28e22","tid":1668622,"uid":81270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T05:47:26.000Z","msg":"大家細心諗下，就知應唔應該出去。<br />\n非分化，但各有各做。"},{"pid":"f0721b00f0fd2d8c4434fb585363eb023f55140e","tid":1668622,"uid":108910,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"加泰"},{"pid":"1c99e8bbdbb5d330580799e4f63a58d45c1b8816","tid":1668622,"uid":207634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f0721b00f0fd2d8c4434fb585363eb023f55140e","tid":1668622,"uid":108910,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"加泰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"c4c62d2eeb1587c182370eec6578ea40303454f4","tid":1668622,"uid":123440,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c99e8bbdbb5d330580799e4f63a58d45c1b8816","tid":1668622,"uid":207634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f0721b00f0fd2d8c4434fb585363eb023f55140e","tid":1668622,"uid":108910,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"加泰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"+1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"+泰"},{"pid":"5768b5678cb14947ddb35e39959b2b113399884b","tid":1668622,"uid":268123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:24:32.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>政治問題</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 重塑公民身分戶口政策保障國家、香港安全和利益<br />\n- 取消18區區議會、建立地域市政議會<br />\n- 禁止公務人員在任前、任內和任後獲港外榮典<br />\n- 改善高鐵一地兩檢操作方式<br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>便民基建</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 修正港鐵、巴士可加可減機制<br />\n- 完善機場集體運輸並加強機場、港珠澳大橋協同發展<br />\n- 興建東鐵、西鐵快速線並完善輕鐵和西鐵聯乘關係<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1VCzpw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1VCzpw.jpg&h=7b29ce56&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RYt8F4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRYt8F4w.jpg&h=eecde813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em><strong>醫療、教育方向</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n- 以減少送院為目標的社區護理服務<br />\n- 重塑教育, 著重知識、技能層次分工<br />\n- 興建至少四所新區域全科醫院<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B2D8F34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB2D8F34.png&h=cb82275f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n求正評及幫推！"},{"pid":"470857bc886d9bbf1cdf9b915541e9dcc0bc9e21","tid":1668622,"uid":131884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4c62d2eeb1587c182370eec6578ea40303454f4","tid":1668622,"uid":123440,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c99e8bbdbb5d330580799e4f63a58d45c1b8816","tid":1668622,"uid":207634,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f0721b00f0fd2d8c4434fb585363eb023f55140e","tid":1668622,"uid":108910,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:20:50.000Z","msg":"加泰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:22:01.000Z","msg":"+1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"+泰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:24:39.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"31e1ab4d81bca2aa8a37770a8e7211353ce9fa72","tid":1668622,"uid":268123,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-22T06:25:21.000Z","msg":"香港 (過到美國人權法嘅話)"},{"pid":"1a17bff5e7d0b1212a0628ebddf11dded7ec4ba1","tid":1668622,"uid":81270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"470857bc886d9bbf1cdf9b915541e9dcc0bc9e21","tid":1668622,"uid":131884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4c62d2eeb1587c182370eec6578ea40303454f4","tid":1668622,"uid":123440,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"1c99e8bbdbb5d330580799e4f63a58d45c1b8816","tid":1668622,"uid":207634,"